about: Discriminator real certainty: 1 (discriminator is taught that real images are 100% real)
Discriminator fake certainty: 0 (discriminator is taught that fake images are 100% fake)
The generator start ok, it mostly generates 1s with little variance and gets better until
epoch ~ 170, where discriminator accuracy on fake images is around 24%.
After ~ epoch 200 the discriminator becomes significantly better than the generator
which negatively impacts the generator, it starts to generate 1, 7, 9 and if trained
long enough it will generate only 1s
1. Use smaller learning rate for the discriminator
2. Make the discriminator uncertain about images (add noise to real/fake images classification)
4. Train the generator more time per epoch than the discriminator
